{"tid":1325722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警闖入港大校園 其實好似吹佢地唔漲","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:15:53.000Z","uid":237628,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbde7713414477fa21d416a7ba2b5c9b2660eea3","tid":1325722,"uid":237628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:23:12.000Z","msg":"其實大學街既範圍係公眾地方，其他大學非教學大樓既範圍都係一樣<br />\n所以只要佢唔係入building既，狗係街道巡邏都吹佢地唔撚漲，就好似我地屌撚左好耐既大陸喱成日係中大同港大觀光既情況一樣。<br />\n即係之前果日同D狗比人屌走同入唔到skylee係因為私人屋苑同Hall係屬於私人地方，佢地冇warrant就入係抵屌，但係如果佢地剩係係大學街到巡邏既就好似係無問題。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過三更半夜黎都不安好心啦，各位HKU同學要小心為上</span></span></strong>，一見到佢地入左building範圍就屌撚走佢地!!!<br />\n有錯請指正，無謂比人帶錯風向!"},{"pid":"f9d648a18b6a01889c33de5c14575771ab1e7a72","tid":1325722,"uid":237628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"642c9e4dd2e6cfe11119dd5f5136457767cf9c72","tid":1325722,"uid":237628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"da7960acc4ac82d083169e73ab10d8155629a9c2","tid":1325722,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"其實中大係全校私家路 不過垃圾奶共校長睬你都傻"},{"pid":"1fca3c2e17a6d86ea1b350a47e8fa78cd180534d","tid":1325722,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"HKU就冇計, 真係公眾路段"},{"pid":"a951a40fe00f47df3675b775323193d30d8f56c0","tid":1325722,"uid":237628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1fca3c2e17a6d86ea1b350a47e8fa78cd180534d","tid":1325722,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"HKU就冇計, 真係公眾路段"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"HKU咁細，連埋Ustreet都唔知有冇CU 4分1咁大"},{"pid":"6c5daf359dc0db9e78dfb16bea9c905bf18d7b20","tid":1325722,"uid":237628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17